org.apache.flex.abc

Class ABCEmitter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.abc.ABCEmitter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IABCVisitor, IVisitor

    public final class ABCEmitter
extends Object
implements IABCVisitor
    The ABCEmitter is an IABCVisitor that collects information about the ABC and emits it as a byte array.
